Package: ecoforge
Version: 0.2
Date: 2024-09-09
Title: A collection of tools for simulating and sampling ecological environments
Author: David Ferrer Ferrando [aut, cre], Javier Fernández-López [aut], Pelayo Acevedo [aut], Pedro Tarroso [aut, cre], 
Maintainer: Pedro Tarroso <ptarroso@cibio.up.pt>
Depends: stats, gstat, terra, spatstat.geom, spatstat.random, knitr
Description: The package offers tools for simulating environments, encompassing both 
  climate and landscape simulations. Additionally, it provides valuable functions for 
  sampling these environments, incorporating random strategies and transects.
